{"tid":2134122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇睇到今期熱血時報（印刷版）封面？？？？？？？","createTime":"2020-07-31T13:05:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T13:42:38.000Z","uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32ba9c465ee7c93d0b93a72c212a039d8181b463","tid":2134122,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"今期封面有逃健 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2Ug0oV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2Ug0oV.jpg&h=cfd90cfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》（印刷版）訂閱連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=d2b5fd99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a>"},{"pid":"95b967bfb352c58252a2394d2224a5af58c98db4","tid":2134122,"uid":33730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntaDui3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntaDui3.jpg&h=56311fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1703ed80311ffc143830283aef75bf95923a630","tid":2134122,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b967bfb352c58252a2394d2224a5af58c98db4","tid":2134122,"uid":33730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntaDui3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntaDui3.jpg&h=56311fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b4d4a61ea7713588dd8bb17be80de7a97f2324","tid":2134122,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b967bfb352c58252a2394d2224a5af58c98db4","tid":2134122,"uid":33730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntaDui3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntaDui3.jpg&h=56311fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c8e5c063f84924456a2547cfd7d314a0c1ea38","tid":2134122,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b967bfb352c58252a2394d2224a5af58c98db4","tid":2134122,"uid":33730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntaDui3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntaDui3.jpg&h=56311fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:23:46.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"8ca3a54878d75fd3b0a2e31a5fd900f5e13c190c","tid":2134122,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"第84期《熱血時報》即將出版。今期封面專訪熱血公民區議員黃兆健，談談他的從政之路，以及參與第七屆立法會直選的因由。<br />\n<br />\n2020年7月18日，熱血公民主席兼立法會議員鄭松泰（泰博），聯同熱血公民區議員黃兆健，以及莊芷茵（法子）、鄭錦滿（四眼），宣佈參與第七屆立法會直選。四位參選者當中，要數兆健最年輕－去年勝出區議會選舉時，不過廿一歲。<br />\n<br />\n「去年承蒙街坊錯愛，當選大埔運頭塘區區議員；今刻我與團隊願承擔更多責任。面對經濟衰退，我們認為即使無法短時間內改變大環境，政府亦必須復興本土在地經濟，讓市民大眾在經濟蕭條下爭取生存空間，能夠自力更生。」<br />\n<br />\n「沒有人天生就懂得政治是甚麼一回事。但我認為『克勤小物』，做好每一件力所能及的事情，即使微不足道，都可以成就大事。」對於時局、對於政治，兆健都侃侃而談，要不是他「和盤托出」，難以想像眼前的他才廿歲出頭。<br />\n<br />\n「過去幾年，大家不是一直都在說『要俾個機會年青人』嗎？今年廿二歲的我，就在大家面前！憑著我的識見與實力，與同道上下一心，定能為香港人謀求福祉。」<br />\n<br />\n如果想收到最新一期《熱血時報》，只要趕在每月27日23時59分前上網訂閱，閣下便會收到即將出版的該期報紙。<br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》（印刷版）訂閱連結︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOZ1DrXAeA17tgS6Eh9jzous%3D&h=d2b5fd99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n把握時代脈搏，掌握最新資訊，讓我們在這個世界熱血地同行。<br />\n#熱血公民 #黃兆健 #選舉廣告"},{"pid":"7b6385f54d61bc938afc3181f12ed1691948f05f","tid":2134122,"uid":122208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"趕客咩印咁大頭<br />\n佢真係以為自己係靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026f4a5db9a21ac2f791fa2b50465a3d451335ea","tid":2134122,"uid":12034,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7b6385f54d61bc938afc3181f12ed1691948f05f","tid":2134122,"uid":122208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:30:47.000Z","msg":"趕客咩印咁大頭<br />\n佢真係以為自己係靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:33:08.000Z","msg":"想証明比人睇自己同選舉主任係唔同人<br />\n<br />\n點知都係無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cb0b3169ee7754090e59982404dbf94020c4cd","tid":2134122,"uid":203393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95b967bfb352c58252a2394d2224a5af58c98db4","tid":2134122,"uid":33730,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ntaDui3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FntaDui3.jpg&h=56311fd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tghZdUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtghZdUk.jpg&h=0cfad708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解佢笑得有種野獸先輩嘅感覺？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8166b6a165cc24183e2def5f2064ebccfd5173"